Text: Roster RequestGentlemen attached is a current roster of WPO Forum Members Please review it carefully and advise of any corrections I would like to email an updated copy of this to you and your assistants by the end of the month Mr Hollingsworth takes over as moderator of the group on January st Mr Everett and Joy have done a wonderful job the past year and are a hard act to follow But I will do my best to keep you all informed Please let me know if there is anything I can do to keep the process running smoothly or assist you in any way Ill take all the help andor suggestions that I can get Donna Baker Group Automotive WPO Forum List xls WPO Forum List xls
